title: El Barista Caffe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, International, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. With no vegetarian or vegan restaurants in town, offers a few vegan choices like a lentil burger, tempura veg and a salad (ask for no cheese), plus a variety of fresh juices. Uses some organic ingredients. Wi-fi. Also is a live music venue. Located opposite the Copec gas station close to the lake shore.
